field_62a1d6835eacb'),(415,22,'faq_group_15_faq_question','I never heard from you that my item has been accepted.'),(416,22,'_faq_group_15_faq_question','field_62a1d6555eaca'),(417,22,'faq_group_15_faq_answer','Please check your spam folder or write us an email at opencall@zero10.app. '),(418,22,'_faq_group_15_faq_answer','field_62a1d6835eacb'),(419,22,'faq_group_16_faq_question','I missed the deadline (or learned too late about Open Call); what should I do?'),(420,22,'_faq_group_16_faq_question','field_62a1d6555eaca'),(421,22,'faq_group_16_faq_answer','Leave your email here (hyperlink), and you’ll be the first to know about upcomingcompetitions.'),(422,22,'_faq_group_16_faq_answer','field_62a1d6835eacb'),(423,22,'faq_group_17_faq_question','I want to see other submissions; where to go?'),(424,22,'_faq_group_17_faq_question','field_62a1d6555eaca'),(425,22,'faq_group_17_faq_answer','All submissions will be published on the Open Call homepage on July 21th.'),(426,22,'_faq_group_17_faq_answer','field_62a1d6835eacb'),(427,22,'faq_group_18_faq_question','How does the voting work?'),(428,22,'_faq_group_18_faq_question','field_62a1d6555eaca'),(429,22,'faq_group_18_faq_answer','Everyone is welcome to participate, so bring your friends and family to vote. Log in with your Facebook or Google account to get started. Then, upvote as many items as you want to. It is not allowed to vote twice for one item and revoke your vote.'),(430,22,'_faq_group_18_faq_answer','field_62a1d6835eacb'),(431,22,'faq_group_19_faq_question','How do you know who has won?'),(432,22,'_faq_group_19_faq_question','field_62a1d6555eaca'),(433,22,'faq_group_19_faq_answer','The authors of the three top-voted items are the three winners of Open Call. Their works will be presented in the ZERO10 app and on the Open Call website after 11th of August. '),(434,22,'_faq_group_19_faq_answer','field_62a1d6835eacb'),(435,22,'faq_group_20_faq_question','I’m a winner! How can I collect my prizes?'),(436,22,'_faq_group_2